                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>If the revenant's murderer dies, the revenant is immediately destroyed. A revenant that can't sense their murderer must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"flat\" data-pf2-dc=\"11\" data-pf2-label=\"Undying Vendetta DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">flat check</span> once every 24 hours to avoid becoming @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Immobilized]{Immobilized} and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Prone]{Prone}; they immediately rise again once they can sense their murderer. A murderer who becomes undead does not trigger the revenant's destruction until the murderer is finally destroyed. The revenant gains a +2 status bonus to checks and DCs against their murderer.</p>"
